00:11:26,380 --> 00:11:28,280
 I just get you to tear yourself apart.

278
00:11:28,280 --> 00:11:33,740
 And my concern is for us in the middle of a culture

279
00:11:33,740 --> 00:11:37,380
 a country, a society that distrusts each other

280
00:11:37,380 --> 00:11:41,420
 and is disintegrating or ripping apart at the seams.

